data.description: Nestled on a spacious lot, this charming home boasts a kitchen featuring granite countertops and an expansive island. Indulge in the spacious primary bedroom with a spa-like ensuite, boasting a separate tub and shower. The split floor plan and 9-foot ceilings enhance the open ambiance, creating an entertainer's delight. Step onto the large covered patio, overlooking a green belt area, seamlessly blending indoor and outdoor living. The expansive backyard, enclosed by a privacy fence, offers a private retreat. With proximity to, Lackland AFB, Sea World, and 1604 Loop, enjoy easy access to sought-after amenities and attractions
